gr.fire.util
Class StringUtil

java.lang.Object
  gr.fire.util.StringUtil

public final class StringUtil
extends java.lang.Object

StringUtil is a utility class that splits a string into lines, according to a specified width. Up until Fire v1.2 this class was called FString

Author:
padeler
